flowchart LR
    A[Input Features: age sex height weight fev1 BMI] --> B[Linear 6 to 64]
    B --> C[BatchNorm1d 64]
    C --> D[ReLU]
    D --> E[Dropout 0.20]
    E --> F[Linear 64 to 32]
    F --> G[ReLU]
    G --> H[Dropout 0.15]
    H --> I[Linear 32 to 16]
    I --> J[ReLU]
    J --> K[Linear 16 to 1 logit]
    K --> L[Sigmoid Probability]
    L --> M{Threshold 0.5}
    M -->|>=0.5| N[High CF Risk]
    M -->|<0.5| O[Lower CF Risk]
